episodes.title: Preaching Out Loud
episodes.plot: The Fab Five help a timid gay pastor who came out in his 30s update his look and find the confidence to lead his congregation into the future.

episodes.title: Groomer Has It
episodes.plot: To get her stalled mobile grooming business back in gear, a scrappy entrepreneur must polish her brand - and add some swag to her own wag.

episodes.plot: A divorced dad who hides behind baggy clothes and crusty hair gel gets a dazzling makeover - and learns to dance - for his daughters wedding day.

episodes.title: The North Philadelphia Story
episodes.plot: He's a humble hero who's survived homelessness - and helped young writers in his community home their voices. Now he's ready for his next chapter.

episodes.title: The Anxious Activist
episodes.plot: A passionate Gen Z activist is so focused on saving the planet that she forgets to schedule self-care. The Fab Five help her find balance.

episodes.title: DJ's on Repeat
episodes.plot: The fab five meet a single DJ who's ready to remaster his life and stop comparing himself to his married siblings.

episodes.title: Silver Lining Sweeney
episodes.plot: A devoted super mom worried about her husband's health slows down to make time for herself and help out her children.

episodes.title: Father Knows Fish
episodes.plot: The Fab Five help a fishmonger and father of three to connect with his family and achieve his dream of opening his very own restaurant.

episodes.title: Paging Dr. Yi
episodes.plot: The Fab Five help a working mother to balance her home life with her career as a paediatrician.

episodes.title: Body Rock or Bust
episodes.plot: His life and his business have seen better days. But this lovable West Philly fitness trainer is finally motivated to whip things back into shape.
